      "description": "The entire Bill of Rights remains a placeholder scaffold with all substantive articles (Scope of Enterprise, Prohibited Activities, Core Identity, Human Authority Reservation, Amendment Protocol, Interpretation Rules) marked as '[To be defined by human principal]'. No identity-defining constraints exist, no prohibited actions are specified, and the organism's foundational boundaries are absent.",
