      "description": "Bill of Rights Article I – Scope of Enterprise is undefined. The scaffold placeholder '[To be defined by human principal]' provides no operational, ethical, or legal boundary for DIO actions. Without a defined enterprise scope, the Arbiter cannot enforce any activity perimeter, leaving the DIO effectively unbounded.",
