    {
      "gap_id": "GAP-BOR-005",
      "description": "Bill of Rights Article V – Amendment Protocol is undefined. The process for human-led BoR modification is missing, blocking any legitimate evolution of the BoR and making the scaffold permanently frozen unless an informal process occurs.",
      "grounding": {
        "document": "Bill of Rights",
        "section_article": "Article V — Amendment Protocol"
