      "gap_id": "GAP-BOR-006",
      "description": "Bill of Rights Article VI – Interpretation Rules is empty. There are no principles or priority rules to resolve ambiguities in the BoR, which would become critical once content is added.",
      "grounding": {
        "document": "Bill of Rights",
        "section_article": "Article VI — Interpretation Rules"
      },
      "priority": {
