      },
      "rationale": "Interpretation rules become important after the BoR has substantive content. Their absence today is a lesser gap, but leaving them undefined risks future inconsistencies in how Nomos and Arbiter adjudicate BoR conflicts, potentially undermining compliance."
    }
  ]
